# TNG QR Print Bridge — Fun Roof (b1) Windows package
# Defense-in-depth secret protection for THIS folder. The bridge root .gitignore
# already ignores these names everywhere, but keep this here too so a real config
# or key dropped in this folder can NEVER be committed by accident.
#
# NOTE: config.example.json is intentionally NOT ignored — it is the template and
# must stay tracked. Only the REAL, filled-in files below are ignored.

# Real, machine-specific config (contains the live business unit / paths)
config.json

# Firebase service-account key — SECRET. Never commit, never email.
service-account.json
*-service-account.json
serviceAccount*.json
*.key
*.pem

# Environment / secret files
.env
.env.*

# Build output & deps (in case anyone runs npm here by mistake)
node_modules/
dist/
daemon/
*.log
